{
  "chapter": 2,
  "chapter_summary": "萧秋水四兄弟击杀符永祥后回到秭归，邓玉函已将符永祥击杀。萧秋水向船主致歉借用龙舟之事，铁衣老翁主动提出护送那锦亮。四人前往五里墟观看龙舟大赛，发现绿舟在终点前故意让蓝舟夺魁。萧秋水等调查得知‘金钱银庄’操控比赛——其后台正是权力帮湖北分舵，由‘铁腕人魔’傅天义掌控。金钱银庄的‘秤千金’和‘管八方’是其得力手下。阿旺、黑老汉等渔民因不服操控而遭蓝衣人殴打，何昆捕头亦不敢深究。萧秋水等人决定管到底，不料阿旺之妻被杀，何昆重伤。萧秋水怒不可遏，率四兄弟闯入金钱银庄，与‘秤千金’正面交锋，一番唇枪舌剑后唐柔以铁蒺藜解围，四人配合无间制服对手。正要了结秤千金时，力大无穷的‘管八方’突然出现。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_deng_yu_han",
      "speaker_name": "邓玉函",
      "listener": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "text": "我本不想杀他，可是他想杀我，我只有杀他。",
      "tone": "冷淡",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "speaker_name": "萧秋水",
      "listener": "char_deng_yu_han",
      "text": "我把他交给你，也是想要你杀他，因为他斫绳毁船，手段大毒，实留不得，你也不必难过。",
      "tone": "理解",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_deng_yu_han",
      "speaker_name": "邓玉函",
      "listener": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "text": "死了",
      "tone": "简洁",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "speaker_name": "萧秋水",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "请问，适才我在此地借用一龙舟，现在搁浅在‘九龙奔江’那儿，烦船主把它起出来，多少费用，在下愿意赔偿。",
      "tone": "客气",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "枯瘦中年人",
      "listener": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "text": "少侠哪里话。诸少侠冒险犯难，仗义除害，本镇的人尚未叩谢大恩，区区破船，又算得了什么？",
      "tone": "感激",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_na_jin_liang",
      "speaker_name": "那锦亮",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "喂，老乡，你的船我买一艘新的给你，就当是这几位少侠赠送的。",
      "tone": "大方",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zuo_qiu_chao_ran",
      "speaker_name": "左丘超然",
      "listener": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "text": "大哥，我们还得看看热闹哩。",
      "tone": "兴致勃勃",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "贫家少年",
      "listener": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "text": "诸位若要看热闹，今日午时本镇龙舟，嘘嘘，十多条龙舟，呜呜哇哇咚咚的，很好很好看的唷，诸位一定要去看……",
      "tone": "讨好",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "speaker_name": "萧秋水",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "谢谢。",
      "tone": "礼貌",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_na_jin_liang",
      "speaker_name": "那锦亮",
      "listener": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "text": "壮士……",
      "tone": "担忧",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_yi_lao_weng",
      "speaker_name": "铁衣老翁",
      "listener": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "text": "萧少侠若有事务，可以先自离去，护送那员外的安危，老朽担了便是。",
      "tone": "豪爽",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_na_jin_liang",
      "speaker_name": "那锦亮",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这，这……",
      "tone": "迟疑",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "speaker_name": "萧秋水",
      "listener": "char_na_jin_liang",
      "text": "这位老前辈，武功比我们加起来都好，你不要担心。",
      "tone": "安慰",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "speaker_name": "萧秋水",
      "listener": "char_a_wang",
      "text": "敢问这位大叔——",
      "tone": "恭敬",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_wang",
      "speaker_name": "阿旺",
      "listener": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "text": "有什么事？",
      "tone": "警惕",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "speaker_name": "萧秋水",
      "listener": "char_a_wang",
      "text": "大叔刚才是绿舟上的好手。偌百余丈的江，大叔多换过三次臂位。歇过一次桨，实在了不起……",
      "tone": "赞赏",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "speaker_name": "萧秋水",
      "listener": "char_a_wang",
      "text": "敢问大叔，为何到了最后终点时忽然放弃了呢？",
      "tone": "疑惑",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_lao_han",
      "speaker_name": "黑老汉",
      "listener": "char_a_wang",
      "text": "阿旺，什么事？他们是谁？",
      "tone": "警觉",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_wang",
      "speaker_name": "阿旺",
      "listener": "char_hei_lao_han",
      "text": "我不知道。",
      "tone": "回避",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "speaker_name": "萧秋水",
      "listener": "char_a_wang",
      "text": "我们没有歹意，大叔你放心，只是心中不解，为何让蓝舟独占鳌头，请大叔们指点迷津而已。",
      "tone": "诚恳",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_wang",
      "speaker_name": "阿旺",
      "listener": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "text": "这不关你们的事，你们少惹麻烦。",
      "tone": "回避",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zuo_qiu_chao_ran",
      "speaker_name": "左丘超然",
      "listener": "char_a_wang",
      "text": "麻烦？有什么麻烦？",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_lao_han",
      "speaker_name": "黑老汉",
      "listener": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "text": "你们是他们派来试探我们是否服气的？",
      "tone": "怀疑",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "speaker_name": "萧秋水",
      "listener": "char_hei_lao_han",
      "text": "他们？他们是谁，什么服气不服气？",
      "tone": "不解",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_lao_han",
      "speaker_name": "黑老汉",
      "listener": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "text": "你们是外省来的公子少爷吧",
      "tone": "确认",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "speaker_name": "萧秋水",
      "listener": "char_hei_lao_han",
      "text": "我们确是外省来的。",
      "tone": "坦诚",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_lao_han",
      "speaker_name": "黑老汉",
      "listener": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "text": "各位小哥有所不知，这种事情你们还是少沾为妙，否则，只怕活不出种归哩。",
      "tone": "警告",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_wang",
      "speaker_name": "阿旺",
      "listener": "char_hei_lao_han",
      "text": "黑哥，不要多说了，祸从口出，唏，还是走吧。",
      "tone": "害怕",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "蓝衣大汉",
      "listener": "char_a_wang",
      "text": "工八乌龟，划了船不回家，在这儿剪舌头，嘀咕些什么？",
      "tone": "粗暴",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_wang",
      "speaker_name": "阿旺",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "没说什么，没说什么。",
      "tone": "害怕",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "蓝衣大汉",
      "listener": "char_a_wang",
      "text": "咄，咄，不说什么，你两个老乡巴还不赶快滚回家去，留在这儿蘑菇些什么！",
      "tone": "威胁",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_lao_han",
      "speaker_name": "黑老汉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "要走我自己会走，不用你推！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "蓝衣大汉",
      "listener": "char_hei_lao_han",
      "text": "哇呵呵，你这是不见棺材不流泪啦，穷发疯呀？",
      "tone": "嚣张",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_wang",
      "speaker_name": "阿旺",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "大爷，大爷莫动气，我揪他回家便是。",
      "tone": "哀求",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "蓝衣大汉",
      "listener": "char_hei_lao_han",
      "text": "要你来多事！看我今天不收拾这黑煤炭，叫他娘生错这粒蛋——",
      "tone": "凶狠",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_wang",
      "speaker_name": "阿旺",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "别，别——",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "speaker_name": "萧秋水",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你们是谁？为何可以随便杀人！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "蓝衣大汉",
      "listener": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "text": "你问阎王老子去吧。",
      "tone": "凶狠",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "蓝衣大汉",
      "listener": "char_zuo_qiu_chao_ran",
      "text": "你是谁？为何要折断我们的手？",
      "tone": "痛苦",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zuo_qiu_chao_ran",
      "speaker_name": "左丘超然",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "回家问你妈妈去吧。",
      "tone": "懒散",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "speaker_name": "萧秋水",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你们走。要是激怒了我们南海邓公子，或者蜀中唐少爷，你们还有得瞧呢！",
      "tone": "威胁",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "何昆",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "什么事？打架吗？不准闹事！",
      "tone": "威严",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "乡民",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "何大人好！",
      "tone": "恭敬",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "何昆",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "怎么了？有什么事？",
      "tone": "询问",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_wang",
      "speaker_name": "阿旺",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "何大爷，我们又遭‘金钱银庄’的人欺负了。",
      "tone": "委屈",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "何昆",
      "listener": "char_a_wang",
      "text": "唉呀，你们怎能跟他们作对呢，好汉不吃眼前亏……",
      "tone": "劝告",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "speaker_name": "萧秋水",
      "listener": "char_a_wang",
      "text": "现在事情已闹到这样，旺叔，黑叔，不如把事情详告我们，也许我们可以替你们解决，否则，他们也不会放过你们的。",
      "tone": "诚恳",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "何昆",
      "listener": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "text": "你们外乡人，哪里知道厉害，强龙不压地头蛇，你们还是快快的回乡去吧。",
      "tone": "劝退",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_rou",
      "speaker_name": "唐柔",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我是四川蜀中，唐家的人。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_deng_yu_han",
      "speaker_name": "邓玉函",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "南海邓玉平的弟弟，邓玉函，便是我。",
      "tone": "冷淡",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zuo_qiu_chao_ran",
      "speaker_name": "左丘超然",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "‘僵尸擒拿手’的二郎折棍法，你要看哪一种擒拿手，我都可以演给你看。",
      "tone": "懒洋洋",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "何昆",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不，不必了。",
      "tone": "惊恐",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "speaker_name": "萧秋水",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我姓萧，何大人要不要验明我的身份？",
      "tone": "自信",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "何昆",
      "listener": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "text": "哦，无须，无须，小的姓何，单名昆字，不知萧公子等侠驾到，真是……",
      "tone": "恭敬",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_wang",
      "speaker_name": "阿旺",
      "listener": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "text": "若萧公子等真要知道此事真相，不如先到舍下一趟，定当详告；但愿萧公子能为我们除此祸害，此处谈话，只怕不便，",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "speaker_name": "萧秋水",
      "listener": "char_a_wang",
      "text": "好。",
      "tone": "果断",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_deng_yu_han",
      "speaker_name": "邓玉函",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "何捕头。",
      "tone": "冷峻",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "何昆",
      "listener": "char_deng_yu_han",
      "text": "有何指教。",
      "tone": "恭敬",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_deng_yu_han",
      "speaker_name": "邓玉函",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "如果你没事，请随我们走一趟，这些地痞生的事，有官府的人插手，比较好办。",
      "tone": "冷静",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "何昆",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我没事。我没事！",
      "tone": "连声",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_deng_yu_han",
      "speaker_name": "邓玉函",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那就去一趟。",
      "tone": "简洁",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_wang",
      "speaker_name": "阿旺",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这些，唉，官府的人不理，报到衙里先抽二十大板，久了也没有报案。官家拿的是权力帮的钱，也就是我们替权力帮熬的血汗，才不管我们的事哩。只有少数几个官爷们，像何大爷、张大爷等，还敢为我们说几句话，抓几个人，别的就不用说了。",
      "tone": "叹息",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "何昆",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "说来惭愧，我们也是受够了压力，抓到的，也只好抓几个喽罗而已；有次我抓了个金钱银庄的小头目，当天晚上就被三个人伏击，腰上挨了一刀，从今之后我也是少惹这些麻烦了。",
      "tone": "惭愧",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zuo_qiu_chao_ran",
      "speaker_name": "左丘超然",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你们可知主持这儿事务的金钱银庄庄主姓什么？样子如何？",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "何昆",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "谁能见过他？我家青天大老爷也只不过见他一二次，而且是黄金白银送去好几次，才得一见哩。至于姓什么……好像是，哦，对了，好像是姓傅的……",
      "tone": "回忆",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "speaker_name": "萧秋水",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "铁腕神魔傅天义？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_deng_yu_han",
      "speaker_name": "邓玉函",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "傅天又是谁？",
      "tone": "不解",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zuo_qiu_chao_ran",
      "speaker_name": "左丘超然",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "在金钱银庄内，傅天义的手下中，可有一位姓程的？",
      "tone": "追问",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "何昆",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "对呀。这人是掌管金钱银庄的财务，据说向来只赚不亏，故人人唤之‘秤千金’，什么生意只要经过他一秤，钱财就会滚滚而来。",
      "tone": "确认",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zuo_qiu_chao_ran",
      "speaker_name": "左丘超然",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "对。‘秤千金’的名字，另从早已忘了，但‘秤千金’却是傅天义手下四名要将之一，另一人姓管……",
      "tone": "补充",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "何昆",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "傅天义在金钱银庄的管理人就是姓‘管’的、人人都叫他做‘管八方’。",
      "tone": "确认",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zuo_qiu_chao_ran",
      "speaker_name": "左丘超然",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这‘秤千金’和‘管八方’都是傅天义手下两大功臣，但更难应付的是其他两人，一名叫‘凶手’，一名叫‘无形’，这两人才是真厉害角色。",
      "tone": "凝重",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "何昆",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "蓝……衣……人……是……金……钱……银……庄……的人下的……手……幸亏我挡……挡了一下……而……你们就……就……就来了……",
      "tone": "奄奄一息",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "speaker_name": "萧秋水",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我要去金钱银庄，你们谁要先回？",
      "tone": "坚定",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_rou",
      "speaker_name": "唐柔",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我要去！",
      "tone": "大声",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_deng_yu_han",
      "speaker_name": "邓玉函",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "去！",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zuo_qiu_chao_ran",
      "speaker_name": "左丘超然",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "吃屎狗才不去！",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "speaker_name": "萧秋水",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "四位想必是权力帮中的金钱银庄分舵里有头有面的人物，但我们找的不是你，冤有头，债有主，叫你们的当家出来。",
      "tone": "从容",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cheng_qian_jin",
      "speaker_name": "秤千金",
      "listener": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "text": "我就是当家的，不知欠你们什么债！",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "speaker_name": "萧秋水",
      "listener": "char_cheng_qian_jin",
      "text": "可是程大老爷？",
      "tone": "确认",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cheng_qian_jin",
      "speaker_name": "秤千金",
      "listener": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "text": "区区人称‘秤千金’便是。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "speaker_name": "萧秋水",
      "listener": "char_cheng_qian_jin",
      "text": "我想请你秤样东西：",
      "tone": "挑衅",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cheng_qian_jin",
      "speaker_name": "秤千金",
      "listener": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "text": "什么东西？",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "speaker_name": "萧秋水",
      "listener": "char_cheng_qian_jin",
      "text": "人头！",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cheng_qian_jin",
      "speaker_name": "秤千金",
      "listener": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "text": "什么人头！",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "speaker_name": "萧秋水",
      "listener": "char_cheng_qian_jin",
      "text": "你的人头。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cheng_qian_jin",
      "speaker_name": "秤千金",
      "listener": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "text": "少年人，你知道这是什么地方？",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "speaker_name": "萧秋水",
      "listener": "char_cheng_qian_jin",
      "text": "‘金钱银庄’。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cheng_qian_jin",
      "speaker_name": "秤千金",
      "listener": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "text": "你可知道‘金钱银庄’的主人是谁？",
      "tone": "威胁",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "speaker_name": "萧秋水",
      "listener": "char_cheng_qian_jin",
      "text": "‘铁腕人魔’傅天义！",
      "tone": "果断",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cheng_qian_jin",
      "speaker_name": "秤千金",
      "listener": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "text": "很好。那你又知道傅爷是谁？",
      "tone": "追问",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "speaker_name": "萧秋水",
      "listener": "char_cheng_qian_jin",
      "text": "‘九天十地，十九人魔’，其中之一地魔。",
      "tone": "了然",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cheng_qian_jin",
      "speaker_name": "秤千金",
      "listener": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "text": "你又知道‘九天十地，十九人魔’，是些什么人组织的？",
      "tone": "追问",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "speaker_name": "萧秋水",
      "listener": "char_cheng_qian_jin",
      "text": "权力帮！",
      "tone": "果断",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cheng_qian_jin",
      "speaker_name": "秤千金",
      "listener": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "text": "你又知道不知道权力帮的地位名声实力？",
      "tone": "追问",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "speaker_name": "萧秋水",
      "listener": "char_cheng_qian_jin",
      "text": "天下第一大帮！",
      "tone": "果断",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cheng_qian_jin",
      "speaker_name": "秤千金",
      "listener": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "text": "那还想怎样？",
      "tone": "反问",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "speaker_name": "萧秋水",
      "listener": "char_cheng_qian_jin",
      "text": "除此祸患！",
      "tone": "激昂",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cheng_qian_jin",
      "speaker_name": "秤千金",
      "listener": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "text": "你既然已知道这些还敢与权力帮作对，我杀了你也好向萧老头交代。",
      "tone": "威胁",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cheng_qian_jin",
      "speaker_name": "秤千金",
      "listener": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "text": "凭你们的道行，要跟大爷我作对还差远呢，还说什么打垮权力帮！",
      "tone": "嚣张",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cheng_qian_jin",
      "speaker_name": "秤千金",
      "listener": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "text": "你们四人，谁最不想死的，只要说出来，我可以最后杀他。",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cheng_qian_jin",
      "speaker_name": "秤千金",
      "listener": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "text": "那我要先杀一个人试试了。",
      "tone": "凶狠",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cheng_qian_jin",
      "speaker_name": "秤千金",
      "listener": "char_tang_rou",
      "text": "看来以后抓到后家的人，还是先杀了再说。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_rou",
      "speaker_name": "唐柔",
      "listener": "char_cheng_qian_jin",
      "text": "可惜唐家的人是抓不到的。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_rou",
      "speaker_name": "唐柔",
      "listener": "char_cheng_qian_jin",
      "text": "这一颗是留给你的。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cheng_qian_jin",
      "speaker_name": "秤千金",
      "listener": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "text": "四位要不要谈生意？",
      "tone": "苦",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zuo_qiu_chao_ran",
      "speaker_name": "左丘超然",
      "listener": "char_cheng_qian_jin",
      "text": "刚才大老板又为何不谈生意？",
      "tone": "悠然",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cheng_qian_jin",
      "speaker_name": "秤千金",
      "listener": "char_zuo_qiu_chao_ran",
      "text": "什么时候？",
      "tone": "假装",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zuo_qiu_chao_ran",
      "speaker_name": "左丘超然",
      "listener": "char_cheng_qian_jin",
      "text": "我们被刀抵着背后的时候。",
      "tone": "悠然",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cheng_qian_jin",
      "speaker_name": "秤千金",
      "listener": "char_zuo_qiu_chao_ran",
      "text": "那是个误会，那实在是个误会。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "speaker_name": "萧秋水",
      "listener": "char_cheng_qian_jin",
      "text": "大老板要谈生意？",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cheng_qian_jin",
      "speaker_name": "秤千金",
      "listener": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "text": "我是生意人，当然要谈生意。",
      "tone": "陪笑",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "speaker_name": "萧秋水",
      "listener": "char_cheng_qian_jin",
      "text": "好，那么我们就来谈生意。",
      "tone": "果断",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cheng_qian_jin",
      "speaker_name": "秤千金",
      "listener": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "text": "不知萧少侠要谈的是什么生意？",
      "tone": "小心",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "speaker_name": "萧秋水",
      "listener": "char_cheng_qian_jin",
      "text": "刚才那桩。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cheng_qian_jin",
      "speaker_name": "秤千金",
      "listener": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "text": "是哪一桩？",
      "tone": "装傻",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "speaker_name": "萧秋水",
      "listener": "char_cheng_qian_jin",
      "text": "人头那一桩。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cheng_qian_jin",
      "speaker_name": "秤千金",
      "listener": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "text": "萧少侠指的是……",
      "tone": "小心",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "speaker_name": "萧秋水",
      "listener": "char_cheng_qian_jin",
      "text": "你的人头！",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cheng_qian_jin",
      "speaker_name": "秤千金",
      "listener": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "text": "在下的人头不卖。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "speaker_name": "萧秋水",
      "listener": "char_cheng_qian_jin",
      "text": "那我就割下你的狗头。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guan_ba_fang",
      "speaker_name": "管八方",
      "listener": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "text": "我也要买人头，你们四只小狗的人头。",
      "tone": "朗声",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zuo_qiu_chao_ran",
      "speaker_name": "左丘超然",
      "listener": "char_guan_ba_fang",
      "text": "管大总管。",
      "tone": "确认",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guan_ba_fang",
      "speaker_name": "管八方",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "正是我管八方。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 2
    }
